<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="1" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="red" WIDTH="150"><B>Conclusion</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Thus we are obliged to remand the case<BR ALIGN='left'/>even though there be findings of fact<BR ALIGN='left'/>which we would consider a foundation for<BR ALIGN='left'/>a proper finding of &quot;business purpose&quot;.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
